We have in our company few spaces in which constantly contents is being changed. In some of them work Bots to update current state of the projects without human interactions (Overwievs, non critical Monitoring).
To have overview of the current situation it is useful to enable daily notifications, however because of number of pages maintained autiomatically, it is not possible to avoid being spammed by those Bot-Changes. It causes that the messages are no more self-speaking/overview.
It would be very useful to be able to i.e. define some users as Bots and add an option to ignore such changes during dialy notification emails as all the changed pages are updated every day and number of interested people is rather small.

