There's the ability to control space templates and global templates, however most useful to me is to control templates across several spaces (as many as 70). I wouldn't want to implement templates individually to all 70 otherwise I'd then have to update them 70 times. This could be simply done by applying templates to certain space categories. Is this already possible and I don't know it? Any work-arounds that I could implement?

